189
00:15:57,120 --> 00:16:01,640
Now that I caught you stealing, I should deal with it for His Highness.

190
00:16:01,640 --> 00:16:04,199
You framed me. Young Master Jiang won't believe you.

191
00:16:04,199 --> 00:16:08,439
You, a thief, how dare you to slander me!

192
00:16:08,439 --> 00:16:12,180
