216
00:17:53,280 --> 00:17:57,140
If your mother knew about this, she would be heartbroken.

217
00:17:57,919 --> 00:18:02,820
Right. I need to stay here until I'm better.

218
00:18:04,919 --> 00:18:06,719
Be nicer.

219
