222
00:18:19,440 --> 00:18:22,800
- Da Fu, Da Fu!
 - Mu Dan.

223
00:18:22,800 --> 00:18:25,520
- Da Fu, let me see where you're hurt.
 - Here.

224
00:18:25,520 --> 00:18:27,520
Has the physician been here? Will it leave a scar?

225
00:18:27,520 --> 00:18:31,180
It's all right, I don't care about it at all.

226
00:18:31,180 --> 00:18:35,119
Master Jiang had it checked and gave me imperial medicine. Don't worry.

227
00:18:35,119 --> 00:18:37,300
