230
00:18:45,140 --> 00:18:48,800
Don't worry, Chuan Yu applied medicine for me.

231
00:18:48,800 --> 00:18:52,100
Go check on Young Master Jiang's back injury.

232
00:18:53,739 --> 00:18:56,119
