I was drunk, not dead. Of course, I remember.

249
00:20:34,040 --> 00:20:38,259
I just drank a bit too much, and only remember a little.

250
00:20:39,680 --> 00:20:45,639
A little is enough. Then, you'll pay the cost of treating the back injury.

251
00:20:51,699 --> 00:20:53,079
Did they really fight?

252
00:20:53,079 --> 00:20:55,839
The door was closed, and there was no sound.

253
00:20:55,839 --> 00:20:59,160
But I saw He Wei Fang return to her courtyard with a stern face.

254
00:20:59,160 --> 00:21:01,859
Once she left, Young Master sent someone to inform us

255
00:21:01,859 --> 00:21:04,960
that he'll rest in your room tonight.

256
00:21:04,960 --> 00:21:08,159
I knew it. Men are never single-minded.

257
00:21:08,159 --> 00:21:12,240
It seems Jiang Residence will be exclusively for you now.

258
00:21:12,240 --> 00:21:15,100
Add more petals to the water, then light all the incense in the room.

259
00:21:15,100 --> 00:21:16,800
Yes.

260
00:21:33,079 --> 00:21:35,480
Quack physician, can't even cure a few rashes!

261
00:21:35,480 --> 00:21:37,800
Madam, these rashes developed strangely.

262
00:21:37,800 --> 00:21:42,380
I heard that He Wei Fang understands some pharmacology. Maybe she's behind this.

263
00:21:42,380 --> 00:21:46,979
Madam, when Young Master comes, you must ask him to stand up for you.

264
00:21:48,800 --> 00:21:50,259
What time is it?

265
00:21:50,259 --> 00:21:52,119
The hour of Xu*.
  (*7:00 p.m - 9:00 p.m.)

266
00:21:52,119 --> 00:21:58,319
If Young Master Jiang sees me like this now, how can I win his favor?

267
00:22:03,520 --> 00:22:07,240
Go tell him, I was very happy to hear he was coming,

268
00:22:07,240 --> 00:22:10,319
but I caught a chill while bathing,

269
00:22:10,319 --> 00:22:14,240
and I'm afraid of infecting him, so please don't visit.

270
00:22:14,240 --> 00:22:18,240
Once I recover, I'll go apologize to him.

271
00:22:18,240 --> 00:22:19,940
Yes.

272
00:22:28,200 --> 00:22:30,119
Madam, do you really want to do this?

273
00:22:30,119 --> 00:22:33,879
I've consulted several physicians, they all said they can't cure it.

274
00:22:33,879 --> 00:22:36,559
What else can I do but plead with her?

275
00:22:36,559 --> 00:22:38,399
What a humiliation.

276
00:22:38,399 --> 00:22:40,760
Haven't I endured enough humiliation already?

277
00:22:40,760 --> 00:22:43,319
What's the harm in enduring it once more?

278
00:22:43,319 --> 00:22:46,440
As long as I can recover my face,

279
00:22:49,050 --> 00:22:51,710
there will be plenty of time to deal with her.

280
00:22:59,240 --> 00:23:03,559
 Sister Mu Dan, could you please meet me?

281
00:23:07,000 --> 00:23:09,319
 Sister Mu Dan?

282
00:23:09,319 --> 00:23:12,340
Madam Lian Zhou, what's the matter?

283
00:23:12,340 --> 00:23:18,399
After bathing with flowers last night, I was covered in itchy rashes.

284
00:23:18,399 --> 00:23:22,960
I know you understand pharmacology. Could you please help me out?

285
00:23:22,960 --> 00:23:28,719
Unfortunately, I heard that Da Fu stole your jewelry, and it's currently under investigation.

286
00:23:28,719 --> 00:23:32,200
Without any leads, I donâ€™t have time to deal with it.

287
00:23:32,200 --> 00:23:36,560
 I... I've made a mistake.

288
00:23:36,560 --> 00:23:40,200
 Miss Zhu Fu didn't steal anything.

289
00:23:42,200 --> 00:23:45,319
In that case, you falsely accused Da Fu.

290
00:23:45,319 --> 00:23:51,319
How will you compensate for the injury to Da Fu's neck and the wrongs suffered?

291
00:23:51,319 --> 00:23:55,040
 I'll explain to the servants and restore Miss Zhu Fu's innocence.

292
00:23:55,040 --> 00:23:59,680
That's what you should do. How is that compensation?

293
00:23:59,680 --> 00:24:05,140
Slander deserves a hundred slaps. This is what you said, right?

294
00:24:13,520 --> 00:24:17,900
Then, please count them, Mu Dan, Miss Zhu Fu.

295
00:24:24,520 --> 00:24:29,480
What trick did you use to make her admit her mistake?

296
00:24:33,280 --> 00:24:37,240
Xiao Chun previously extracted a lot of flower juice for the beauty pills.

297
00:24:37,240 --> 00:24:42,680
She discovered that mixing several types of flower juices can cause rashes.

298
00:24:42,680 --> 00:24:44,479
Though there's no danger to life,

299
00:24:44,479 --> 00:24:48,680
it can damage one's appearance and cause unbearable itching.

300
00:24:48,680 --> 00:24:52,319
So, I took some and put it in her bathtub.

301
00:25:02,200 --> 00:25:06,599
You framed her for theft, now you deserve what you did.

302
00:25:06,599 --> 00:25:11,680
You need to write a statement of apology and put it in the hall to apologize to Zhu Fu.

303
00:25:14,259 --> 00:25:20,680
Okay, I'll write it later. Sister, can you give me the antidote recipe?

304
00:25:21,499 --> 00:25:24,119
I don't know your past,

305
00:25:24,119 --> 00:25:29,500
but I can tell you didn't want to marry into this family.

306
00:25:29,500 --> 00:25:32,079
You must have your grievances and helplessness,

307
00:25:32,079 --> 00:25:35,559
so want to secure something at the Jiang Residence to rely on.

308
00:25:35,559 --> 00:25:38,880
It's reasonable and I can understand it.

309
00:25:39,520 --> 00:25:45,000
I'm focused solely on business and don't want to fight for anything with you.

310
00:25:45,000 --> 00:25:49,000
If you no longer harm my close friends and family,

311
00:25:49,000 --> 00:25:52,800
we can still live in peace as we did before.

312
00:25:52,800 --> 00:25:55,120
Focused solely on business?

313
00:25:56,460 --> 00:25:59,250
Don't you care about Young Master Jiang's affections?

314
00:26:00,440 --> 00:26:07,280
Sui Zhi and I are mutually in love, so I don't need to fight for anything.

315
00:26:07,839 --> 00:26:11,960
Instead of wasting time here, you should treat yourself better.

316
00:26:11,960 --> 00:26:13,560
You!

317
00:26:17,399 --> 00:26:20,939
Don't get upset over a man who doesn't care about you.

318
00:26:21,620 --> 00:26:27,280
The madder you get, the harder it'll be for the rashes to subside.

319
00:26:27,280 --> 00:26:32,140
Temper justice with mercy. You're truly something.

320
00:26:33,559 --> 00:26:40,300
The world is harsh for us women, why employ tricks to harm each other?

321
00:26:41,300 --> 00:26:44,270
You're the adopted daughter of Prince Ning.

322
00:26:44,270 --> 00:26:48,639
Besides your beauty, you must have other remarkable qualities.

323
00:26:48,639 --> 00:26:54,528
Is there nothing else you want to do besides pleasing your husband?

324
00:27:00,824 --> 00:27:05,680
I have many exceptionally talented women here. They've long escaped the inner chambers.

325
00:27:05,680 --> 00:27:13,519
Now, they're all enjoying their lives embroidering, gardening, crafting, and dressing up.

326
00:27:13,519 --> 00:27:19,420
If you're interested in gardening, you can come visit my garden.

327
00:27:20,599 --> 00:27:26,280
You want me to grow flowers and do business with you?

328
00:27:26,280 --> 00:27:28,680
Anything wrong with that?

329
00:27:29,319 --> 00:27:33,079
You're so strange, married to Floral Envoy,

330
00:27:33,079 --> 00:27:36,780
yet still working hard to earn small amounts of money.

331
00:27:36,780 --> 00:27:43,060
I truly don't understand why Young Master Jiang's so devoted to you.

332
00:27:44,699 --> 00:27:48,559
What's wrong with earning money? Who would refuse money?

333
00:27:48,559 --> 00:27:52,960
Besides, he likes me for having such abilities.

334
00:27:52,960 --> 00:27:55,140
Don't be arrogant.

335
00:27:56,399 --> 00:28:00,060
Apply it three times a day, and you'll be cured in seven days.

336
00:28:00,520 --> 00:28:04,399
Think about what I've told you today.

337
00:28:04,399 --> 00:28:08,559
If you figure it out, you can come to me anytime.

338
00:28:31,520 --> 00:28:37,860
 I truly don't understand why Young Master Jiang's so devoted to you.

339
00:28:39,319 --> 00:28:44,260
 We acted so well that Lian Zhou would say that.

340
00:28:51,119 --> 00:28:53,520
 Dusk.

341
00:28:54,668 --> 00:28:56,580

342
00:28:57,780 --> 00:28:59,680
Oh, no.

343
00:29:05,960 --> 00:29:08,940
Brother Jiang, I toast to you.

344
00:29:16,060 --> 00:29:19,680
They all say the newly appointed Deputy Transport Officer is strict and fair.

345
00:29:19,680 --> 00:29:21,559
Brother Qi, you should drink less.

346
00:29:21,559 --> 00:29:27,000
If you come to work with the smell of alcohol tomorrow, I'm afraid you'll get scolded.

347
00:29:27,499 --> 00:29:30,399
I didn't have much work before.

348
00:29:30,399 --> 00:29:35,439
Since Liu Chang came, he's been strict and fair, showing no mercy at all.

349
00:29:35,439 --> 00:29:39,440
We're so busy that we can't even take a break.

350
00:29:39,440 --> 00:29:43,319
Liu Chang is just Prince Ning's live in son-in-law,

351
00:29:43,319 --> 00:29:46,959
and a pedantic scholar from a humble background.

352
00:29:46,959 --> 00:29:48,839
What can he achieve?

353
00:29:48,839 --> 00:29:50,919
He really has high ambitions.

354
00:29:50,919 --> 00:29:54,359
Repairing docks and consolidating fleets.

355
00:29:54,359 --> 00:30:00,280
I think he won't stop until he shows Prince Ning some achievements.

356
00:30:00,280 --> 00:30:05,319
Brother Zi Shu is working so hard, is he aiming for promotion orâ€¦

357
00:30:05,319 --> 00:30:10,119
Who doesn't want a promotion? But benefits must still be secured.

358
00:30:10,119 --> 00:30:16,960
Otherwise, Liu Chang's meager salary cannot support the noble Princess.

359
00:30:16,960 --> 00:30:21,919
Despite complaining, you still diligently follow Zi Shu's lead.

360
00:30:21,919 --> 00:30:27,000
Brother Qi, the jade pendant you're wearing today is probably worth a year's salary.

361
00:30:28,979 --> 00:30:31,409
It's better to share the joy than enjoy alone.

362
00:30:31,409 --> 00:30:33,839
With such a lucrative opportunity,

363
00:30:33,839 --> 00:30:37,599
Brother Qi, why don't you come to my residence tomorrow and tell me?

364
00:30:37,599 --> 00:30:39,780
My pleasure!

365
00:30:44,919 --> 00:30:51,499
I think the jade on Young Master's waist looks even better.

366
00:30:55,119 --> 00:30:58,240
A precious jade matches a beauty well.

367
00:30:58,240 --> 00:30:59,960
Thank you, Young Master.

368
00:30:59,960 --> 00:31:04,659
Wait, Young Master Jiang. You promised to give me a bracelet.

369
00:31:04,659 --> 00:31:07,159
You mustn't be biased.

370
00:31:19,019 --> 00:31:22,810
It's late, just drinking isn't fun.

371
00:31:22,810 --> 00:31:27,410
How about blowing out a few candles?

372
00:31:28,219 --> 00:31:34,200
What's the hurry on such a long night? We haven't even finished enjoying the wine.

373
00:31:35,079 --> 00:31:40,860
Even if it's just a social, he doesn't have to hold women like this.

374
00:31:43,639 --> 00:31:48,879
With what Lian Zhou thinks, she surely hasn't seen Jiang Chang Yang this way.

375
00:31:50,919 --> 00:31:55,580
I knew it. I almost got confused by Lian Zhou.

376
00:32:06,760 --> 00:32:10,879
Jiang Sui Zhi, it's so late. Why haven't you gone home?

377
00:32:10,879 --> 00:32:15,340
If you want to drink, I can accompany you.

378
00:32:17,760 --> 00:32:22,240
You're busy with business, yet you surprisingly had time to pick me up today.

379
00:32:22,240 --> 00:32:25,739
Then, of course, I should drink with you.

380
00:32:26,599 --> 00:32:30,919
Brother Qi, pay attention to the business we discussed.

381
00:32:30,919 --> 00:32:33,480
My beloved is picking me up, so I'm leaving.

382
00:32:33,480 --> 00:32:35,539
Brother Sui Zhi, youâ€¦

383
00:32:35,539 --> 00:32:41,720
Recently, Floral Haven released new sachets. Try it.

384
00:32:41,720 --> 00:32:44,760
The rouge scent from Huanyun Tower is too strong.

385
00:32:44,760 --> 00:32:50,600
With these, you can avoid interrogation from wives and concubines at home.

386
00:32:50,600 --> 00:32:52,220
Right?

387
00:32:52,800 --> 00:32:54,600
Farewell.

388
00:33:10,760 --> 00:33:12,240
What's going on?

389
00:33:12,240 --> 00:33:15,080
You said you'd rescue me at first quarter of Xu Hour, but you arrived at the third.

390
00:33:15,080 --> 00:33:18,440
If you were any later, the candles in the room would've been blown out.

391
00:33:18,939 --> 00:33:21,809
I got frightened by Lian Zhou.

392
00:33:21,809 --> 00:33:25,840
We acted too well. Lian Zhou truly thinks you've fallen for me.

393
00:33:25,840 --> 00:33:31,319
She even... told me a bunch of strange words.

394
00:33:31,319 --> 00:33:36,440
She should really see your flirtatious behavior today.

395
00:33:37,919 --> 00:33:43,739
Just take what she said as a joke. You didn't take it seriously, did you?

396
00:33:47,419 --> 00:33:49,920
Of course, I didn't.

397
00:33:49,920 --> 00:33:52,319
Lian Zhou only sees how good you treat me.

398
00:33:52,319 --> 00:33:57,340
She doesn't know that it's because we have a life-and-death friendship.

399
00:33:57,920 --> 00:34:01,559
But, understandably, outsiders wouldn't understand

400
00:34:01,559 --> 00:34:05,499
why a high-ranking official treat a small merchant so well?

401
00:34:11,280 --> 00:34:13,240
Over the years,

402
00:34:14,380 --> 00:34:19,800
I've seen a lot of intrigues in officialdom and the pretenses between people.

403
00:34:20,380 --> 00:34:24,680
Someone as honest and open-minded as you is rare.

404
00:34:24,680 --> 00:34:28,280
Of course, I would treat you sincerely.

405
00:34:32,040 --> 00:34:37,019
Are you drunk? Why are you suddenly praising me?

406
00:34:37,019 --> 00:34:40,620
Making me feel quite embarrassed.

407
00:34:41,280 --> 00:34:44,559
You're this type of person, so you deserves others' kindness.

408
00:34:44,559 --> 00:34:48,419
Moreover, you also treat me well.

409
00:34:48,919 --> 00:34:50,750
You said before,

410
00:34:51,870 --> 00:34:56,690
it's hard to find a soulmate. There's no need to always express gratitude.

411
00:34:56,690 --> 00:34:58,920
It makes us seem distant.

412
00:35:01,200 --> 00:35:05,979
You treat me sincerely, I'll never let you down as a soulmate.

413
00:35:05,979 --> 00:35:09,319
From now on, in my heart, besides Da Fu and Xiao Chun,

414
00:35:09,319 --> 00:35:12,560
you're my most important person.

415
00:35:12,560 --> 00:35:15,639
If you need help, just tell me.

416
00:35:17,280 --> 00:35:24,240
Jiang Xiao Hua, we're soulmates, and I only rank third in your heart?

417
00:35:24,240 --> 00:35:26,959
Naturally, besties are more important.

418
00:35:43,839 --> 00:35:45,390
Here.

419
00:35:47,219 --> 00:35:50,219
- Take the prescription to get the medicine.
 - Thank you.

420
00:35:56,039 --> 00:35:58,760
Have all the gifts from clients been returned?

421
00:35:58,760 --> 00:36:02,080
Madam Luo, who came before, embroidered this handkerchief to show her gratitude.

422
00:36:02,080 --> 00:36:06,080
This isn't any precious item, and with your name,

423
00:36:06,080 --> 00:36:08,459
so I decided to keep it.

424
00:36:12,720 --> 00:36:17,160
Her eye condition just improved. She shouldn't do such taxing things.

425
00:36:17,160 --> 00:36:20,639
When she comes next, I'll give her a good talking to.

426
00:36:21,879 --> 00:36:24,039
Please call the next person.

427
00:36:24,039 --> 00:36:25,639
Yes.

428
00:36:35,939 --> 00:36:37,539
Father.

429
00:36:40,120 --> 00:36:41,839
Young Master Liu, remember.

430
00:36:41,839 --> 00:36:46,319
Spring is not yet full, and crops are already growing. That's Qin.

431
00:36:47,680 --> 00:36:50,459
I taught your sister like this, too.

432
00:36:51,170 --> 00:36:54,270

433
00:37:04,160 --> 00:37:05,900
Right.

434
00:37:05,900 --> 00:37:08,910
Young Master Liu, you're holding the brush wrong again.

435
00:37:08,919 --> 00:37:11,280
Look, hold the brush like this,

436
00:37:11,280 --> 00:37:14,519
only then will the strokes you write be proper.

437
00:37:14,519 --> 00:37:17,519
See? Here, try again.

438
00:37:18,600 --> 00:37:19,760
Yes.

439
00:37:19,760 --> 00:37:22,200
Combine these two. Move this back.

440
00:37:22,200 --> 00:37:24,719
Okay, try it now.

441
00:37:25,879 --> 00:37:28,360
Find the feeling.

442
00:37:28,360 --> 00:37:31,390
Not bad. Right.

443
00:37:32,160 --> 00:37:33,960
Go further down.

444
00:37:36,800 --> 00:37:38,500
Mu Dan.

445
00:37:40,879 --> 00:37:42,860
Why are you here at this hour?

446
00:37:42,860 --> 00:37:46,760
- Continue.
 - You helped Consort Shu recuperate for a while, and she's improved a lot.

447
00:37:46,760 --> 00:37:50,080
Before returning to the palace, she asked me to give you this painting.

448
00:37:50,080 --> 00:37:53,599
To thank you for your companionship during this time.

449
00:37:54,519 --> 00:37:57,870
She paid me for those medicinal herbs and supplies.

450
00:37:57,870 --> 00:38:00,670
Why is Consort Shu so polite?

451
00:38:07,479 --> 00:38:11,720
You often ride with Consort Shu. Your polo skills must have improved a lot.

452
00:38:11,720 --> 00:38:15,519
Of course, do you dare compete with me someday?

453
00:38:15,519 --> 00:38:19,160
How bold, do you dare bet on it?

454
00:38:19,160 --> 00:38:23,080
Isn't the interest you've collected from me enough? Want to swindle me for more?

455
00:38:23,080 --> 00:38:24,759
Don't even think about it.

456
00:38:24,759 --> 00:38:27,280
Consort Shu has given you her well-bred horse.

457
00:38:27,280 --> 00:38:30,540
With a fine horse, are you still afraid to lose?

458
00:38:32,240 --> 00:38:35,919
Consort Shu has never looked down on me because of my rank.

459
00:38:35,919 --> 00:38:38,139
She treats me well.

460
00:38:39,399 --> 00:38:43,120
Now that she has returned, it's not as comfortable or free.

461
00:38:43,120 --> 00:38:47,760
Could you persuade His Majesty to visit her more often?

462
00:38:47,760 --> 00:38:50,359
At least let her see her child more often.

463
00:38:50,359 --> 00:38:52,879
Don't worry, Consort Shu has been away from the palace for a while.

464
00:38:52,879 --> 00:38:56,740
His Majesty also misses her greatly and will surely treat her well.

465
00:38:57,340 --> 00:39:01,890
Sister, I've written another character, please check if it's correct.

466
00:39:01,890 --> 00:39:03,530

467
00:39:04,719 --> 00:39:08,280
I never taught you this character, how did you learn it?

468
00:39:08,280 --> 00:39:12,039
I've been observing Fragrant Garden's plaque every day,

469
00:39:12,039 --> 00:39:14,399
so I learned to write it.

470
00:39:14,399 --> 00:39:19,560
Young Master Liu is smart. I'll teach you another character then.

471
00:39:19,560 --> 00:39:21,560
The Garden in Fragrance Garden.

472
00:39:22,240 --> 00:39:23,740
Here.

473
00:39:34,019 --> 00:39:35,919
I'll write the outer part.

474
00:39:39,439 --> 00:39:41,239
Give it a try.

475
00:39:43,879 --> 00:39:45,560
Young Master Liu is clever,

476
00:39:45,560 --> 00:39:49,680
but Mu Dan is busy with business and can't teach you every day.

477
00:39:49,680 --> 00:39:53,860
How about I find you a private tutor?

478
00:39:53,860 --> 00:39:58,640
I don't want any tutor, having Sister teach me is enough.

479
00:39:58,640 --> 00:40:04,219
I only like to cook, and I'm not cut out for studying or being an official.

480
00:40:04,820 --> 00:40:08,760
Becoming an official isn't the only path to success.

481
00:40:08,760 --> 00:40:12,839
If you like cooking, I can hire a restaurant chef for you.

482
00:40:12,839 --> 00:40:17,640
Learn from him for a few years, and then you can open your own restaurant.

483
00:40:17,640 --> 00:40:18,680
Iâ€¦

484
00:40:18,680 --> 00:40:22,479
I heard that Prosperity House's Chef Xue plans to take on an apprentice this year.

485
00:40:22,479 --> 00:40:25,680
Really? That would be great.

486
00:40:25,680 --> 00:40:28,479
Do you know him? Could you introduce him?

487
00:40:28,479 --> 00:40:31,280
I can take Young Master Liu to visit him.

488
00:40:31,280 --> 00:40:33,180
No problem.

489
00:40:34,200 --> 00:40:39,439
Sister, I've heard Floral Envoy enjoys painting the beauties of Huanyun Tower.

490
00:40:39,439 --> 00:40:43,080
Can you have Floral Envoy paint one of us?

